package: brief description

Leave a blank line and then put the full details here. No line should
exceed 72 characters in length. The brief description should be
something like "upgraded packageX to versionY" or 
"fixed CVE-2019-12345".

When referencing external links, use the following format:

For more information see:
	https://example.com/reference1
	https://example.net/reference2

If this commit is a security fix, make sure to include the relevant
CVE ids in the commit message. Also make this the last line of the
message:

* SECURITY FIX *

